the associated press erroneously reported june 26 that new 
mexico lobbyist edwin t mahrs firm spent 1 million in 198789 on 
lobbying the new mexico legislature and misattributed to him an 
estimate that 80 percent of the spending was for entertainment the 
1 million was the total spending reported by all new mexico 
