extended delaying the wreathlaying ceremony by about three hours 
mandela has at times canceled events to rest during his grueling 
14nation tour of europe and north america a downpour soaked the 
1300 people waiting near kings crypt a carnival atmosphere set 
in when the rain stopped complete with popcorn vendors and music 
from a military band 
