1986 ruling that he had been subjected to double jeopardy the 
supreme court reversed that ruling and reinstated the death 
sentence by a 54 vote in 1987 
the 9th circuit then considered other issues raised by adamsons 
case and once again threw out his death sentence 
the case is lewis vs adamson 881553 
