and take good care of the national flag which shows four small and 
one large yellow star against a red field 
the large star stands for the communist party and the small 
stars represent various classes in chinese society the red color 
represents the communist revolution 
the law says chinas flag since the communist takeover in 1949 
must be raised every day on tiananmen square at the gate to the 
communist headquarters of zhongnanhai in front of various 
government and party offices and at ports airports and border 
railway stations 
