bonds for purchase of wetlands beaches scenic river areas and 
forests the 30 million would be raised by taxing realestate 
transfers and investments 
the republican governor signed the measure while on a 
reelection campaign stop in west palm beach 
preservation 2000 is the most ambitious land acquisition 
program in the nation and will enable florida to lead the way in 
protecting its environment for future generations martinez said 
