stage work and spent five years as an aerialist with circuses in 
switzerland sweden japan australia and south america she worked 
as a substitute with the flying gaonas and her daughter lesley 
aletter often worked with her 
i wasnt a gymnast said meriwether i did the simple 
tricks but lesley could do the unusual tricks 
lesley currently works as a film editor another daughter kyle 
aletter is an actress meriwether is married to marshall borden 
an actor writer and director and they frequently have worked 
together in regional theater 
