co during a meeting here 
nissan japans second largest automaker is fujis largest 
shareholder with a 42 percent stake and its superior in a 
corporate grouping or keiretsu japan has many such groups bound 
together by cross shareholdings other financial ties and common 
business strategies 
fuji would have been probably taken over if it were in the 
